index.introduction: F-Droid d akatalug yettwasebdaden n yisnasen n iseγzanen illelliyen neγ n uγbalu yeldin γef tetiknulujit Android. Amsaγ ad yessifses tunigin, asebded akked uḍfaṛ n ileqman γef yibenk-ik.

package.signed_by_fdroid: Yebna udiγ yezmel sγur F-Droid, yettwaḍmen akken ad imeγru d d uγbalu-agi n uγbaṛ.
package.suggest_downloading_via_fdroid: Γas akken asider n APK yella ddaw-a, ẓer d akken ma tesbeddeḍ asnas s tarrayrt-agi, ur d-tremseḍ ara ar zdat ilγa udiq d tarrayt ur nerkid ara i usider. Yelha limer ad tesbeddeḍ amsaγ F-Droid i waya.
